data.description:
Don't wait to set up a showing to see this beautiful spacious 3,766 SQFT home! 4 bedrooms/3.5 bath 
A large den, a fifth room off the den that could be used as an office, man cave, etc., large laundry room, and lots of closet and storage space throughout the home! A nice 2 vehicle garage. A shed/workshop in the fenced back yard. This home in conveniently located in town but still gives you a quiet setting! 
More interior pictures coming soon!
